r way might be a little foolhardy \\\"An Olympic Scene Draws Scorn.\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1472, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1132, \"end\": 1145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sasha_Grishin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sasha Grishin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sasha_Grishin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sasha_Grishin\"}, {\"begin\": 1180, \"end\": 1210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_National_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian National University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_National_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_National_University\"}, {\"begin\": 1221, \"end\": 1239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_New_York_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.849179262473671e-24, \"text\": \"The New York Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_New_York_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_New_York_Times\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Art historian\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"professor emeritus\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1172}, {\"ngram\": \"The idea\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"the central figure\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"a halo\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1287}, {\"ngram\": \"a group\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1299}, {\"ngram\": \"followers\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1312}, {\"ngram\": \"either side\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"The Last Supper' iconography\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"any other way\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"a little foolhardy \\\"An Olympic Scene Draws Scorn\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Did it Really Parody 'The Last Supper?\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\